  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/69c64897f122b75ecc7e34157951773c.avif?t=1570048563\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>Neverliria is a survival sandbox game, where you play for the fire-headed girl, lost in a fantasy forest full of shadows and dangers.<br>The most reliable way of protecting yourself from the darkness is light (of the campfire or your own hand-held phoenix) or ... a perfect arrow of the faithful servant-dwarf.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/14b6793d2813292e5b74d9a1c5c13c09.poster.avif?t=1570048563\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/14b6793d2813292e5b74d9a1c5c13c09.webm?t=1570048563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/14b6793d2813292e5b74d9a1c5c13c09.mp4?t=1570048563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Neverliria you will have a unique survival game experience, where resources are more than typical wood or stone, but also fantastic creatures and magic items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/c67ba137a394ae7788d57c18f72d0920.avif?t=1570048563\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>* 20 types of buildings available for construction and improvement.<br>* Lots of resources and unique items that give new opportunities for development.<br>* Procedurally generated world filled with many fantastic places and creatures.<br>* Create sources of light and get the support of the allies to protect yourself from the forces of darkness!<br>* Beautiful pixel stylistics.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/69c64897f122b75ecc7e34157951773c.avif?t=1570048563\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>Neverliria is a survival sandbox game, where you play for the fire-headed girl, lost in a fantasy forest full of shadows and dangers.<br>The most reliable way of protecting yourself from the darkness is light (of the campfire or your own hand-held phoenix) or ... a perfect arrow of the faithful servant-dwarf.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/14b6793d2813292e5b74d9a1c5c13c09.poster.avif?t=1570048563\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/14b6793d2813292e5b74d9a1c5c13c09.webm?t=1570048563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/14b6793d2813292e5b74d9a1c5c13c09.mp4?t=1570048563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Neverliria you will have a unique survival game experience, where resources are more than typical wood or stone, but also fantastic creatures and magic items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904890/extras/c67ba137a394ae7788d57c18f72d0920.avif?t=1570048563\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>* 20 types of buildings available for construction and improvement.<br>* Lots of resources and unique items that give new opportunities for development.<br>* Procedurally generated world filled with many fantastic places and creatures.<br>* Create sources of light and get the support of the allies to protect yourself from the forces of darkness!<br>* Beautiful pixel stylistics.",
